asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

name: DJ Myxxi Tryxx
description: Myxomatosis OHare grew up in the suburbs.The daughter of an affluent middle class family.Her father was strict  devoutly religious.Her mother was a timid wife who always obeyed her husbands wishes.Myxxi was sent to a private all girls boarding school when she turned 13.She hated the discipline  rigid structure both at school  at home.Some nights, she would sneak out of her dorm room with a couple of her school friends  they would go to late night rave parties.It was at these events where she would develop a love of EDM.In her final year of school she was caught sneaking back into her dorm room, after a late night rave  she was expelled.Her father was furious but by this time she had already decided that she wanted to become a DJ.She left home to pursue her dream.She is now a successful DJ performing under the name of DJ Myxxi Tryxx. She has a long on again off again relationship with Leapus Leporidae.Whilst they seem to love each other it also seems that they both have a fear of commitment.

name: Brian “Cocktail” Flanagan
description:
As a young rabbit, Cocktail longed for a high powered career in the business world. Having grown up in a working-class burrow, he put himself through school and sought opportunities in New York City. 

Unable to make inroads, he began bartending and discovered a knack for twirling and tossing bottles in the air, entertaining female bunny customers with his charm (and stylish dress — not to mention his flower wreath crown). 

Cocktail moved to Jamaica to save money to open his own bar; while there he fell in love with a beautiful artist. He spends his nights tending bar and his days playing beach volleyball.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
